http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/For-100-panchayats/article14006655.ece

Hundred panchayats across 14 districts in the State would achieve complete e-literacy by March 31, Minister for Panchayats M.K. Muneer has said.He was speaking after inaugurating a seminar on e-literacy organised here by the P. N. Panicker Foundation. He said e-literacy was the need of the hour and the empowerment of grama sabhas and panchayats through e-literacy would make their functioning more transparent and people-friendly, a press note quoted him as saying.Former MP Pannian Ravindran presided over the inaugural function.